data.description: **$5,000 CREDIT AT CLOSING** HOME & TERMITE INSPECTIONS ALONG WITH VA APPRAISAL ON FILE & AT VALUE! Welcome to your new abode - a charming & classic ranch-style home nestled in a cul-de-sac in the Cottonade subdivision. Upon entering the home you are greeted by a large open concept with a newly-renovated brick fireplace, vinyl floors throughout, & beautiful bay windows. The dining room/kitchen combo features modern light fixtures, access to the back deck, granite countertops, & an elegant tile backsplash. A split floor plan leads you into a large primary suite with built-in shelving, closet space, ample natural lighting, & a massive tiled walk-in shower with LED lighting. Three additional beds, a full bath, & a second suite. Journey to the large, fenced-in backyard with a massive, partially covered, two-level back deck, & shed - the perfect space to entertain your guests year-round! With just a short commute to Fort Liberty, local shops and restaurants, this beauty won't last long!
